#  Student Placement Prediction with Model Comparison & Feature Analysis

This project is a complete Machine Learning application that predicts whether a student is likely to get placed by comparing multiple classification algorithms and selecting the best-performing model.

The project also provides feature importance analysis, probability-based predictions, visualization, and model persistence.

---

##  Features

- Compare multiple Machine Learning algorithms
  - Logistic Regression
  - Decision Tree Classifier
  - Random Forest Classifier
- Automatic model evaluation
- Student placement prediction
- Probability-based prediction
- Feature Importance Analysis
- Accuracy comparison
- Classification Report
- Confusion Matrix
- Data visualization using Matplotlib
- Save and load trained model using Joblib
- User input validation and error handling

---

##  Technologies Used

- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Scikit-learn
- Joblib

