##  Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/student-placement-prediction-model-comparison-and-feature-analysis.git
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install pandas matplotlib scikit-learn joblib
```

Run the project:

```bash
python main.py
```

